%% Invize System Flows - Current + Future State
%% Render each block independently in Mermaid-compatible viewers.

%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
%% DIAGRAM 1: End-to-End Request, Auth, and Data Access (Improved)
%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
flowchart LR
    U[👤 User] --> FE[🖥️ Next.js UI\nDashboard, Invoices, Queue, Payments, Admin]
    FE --> MW[🛡️ Next Middleware\nRoute guard + token cookie checks]
    MW -->|valid session| GW[🔀 API Gateway\napp/api/[[...path]] proxy]
    MW -->|missing token| L[🔐 Login/Register page]

    L --> AUTH1[🔑 Auth API\n/login /register /refresh /logout]
    AUTH1 --> TOK[🎟️ JWT + Refresh Rotation]
    TOK --> MW

    GW --> RID[🧾 FastAPI Request-ID Middleware]
    RID --> RT[⚙️ Domain Routers\nAuth Users Integrations Docs Workflow Payments Admin]

    RT --> DB[(🗄️ Prisma + Mongo Models)]
    RT --> FS[(📁 Job status/result files)]
    RT --> AI[🤖 AI Services\nExtraction + Suggestions]
    RT --> ERP[🏢 ERP Adapter Layer\nDemo/REST/Stub]

    DB --> RT
    FS --> RT
    AI --> RT
    ERP --> RT
    RT --> GW --> FE --> U

%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
%% DIAGRAM 2: Invoice Intelligence Pipeline + Operational Decisions
%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
flowchart TD
    A[📄 Analyst uploads invoice] --> B[✅ File validation\nsize/type]
    B --> C[🧵 Create job + persist initial status]
    C --> D[⏳ Background task started]

    D --> E[🔍 OCR stage]
    E --> F[🧠 Field extraction + normalization]
    F --> G[🛡️ Verification/Compliance\nDuplicate + Authenticity + Audit]
    G --> H[🔗 ERP matching\nPO/GRN/vendor checks]

    H --> I{⚠️ Exception classified?}
    I -- Yes --> J[📥 Create review queue item]
    I -- No --> K[✅ Mark ready for approval]

    J --> J1[👩‍💼 Ops triage queue]
    J1 --> J2[📝 Add notes and resolve]
    J2 --> L{Decision}

    K --> L
    L -- Approve --> M[👍 Update approval summary]
    L -- Reject --> N[❌ Update rejection summary]

    M --> O[💳 Payment readiness engine]
    N --> P[🔁 Return to correction/reprocess path]
    O --> Q[🧾 Batch creation + line items]
    Q --> R[🚀 Batch submission]
    R --> S[🏦 Treasury stub / payout processor]
    S --> T[(🗄️ Batch + settlement states)]

%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
%% DIAGRAM 3: Admin, Governance, Security, and Audit Control Plane
%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
flowchart TB
    AD[🧑‍💼 Admin] --> UI[⚙️ Admin + Settings UI]

    UI --> UMG[👥 User Management\ninvite, activate/deactivate, role updates]
    UI --> SEC[🛡️ Security Controls\nsession policy, token policy]
    UI --> INT[🔌 Integrations Control\nerp_type and external configs]
    UI --> AUD[📜 Audit Views\nsecurity events + action trails]
    UI --> SYS[📈 System Health/Stats]

    UMG --> APIA[⚙️ Administration Router]
    SEC --> APIA
    INT --> APII[⚙️ Integrations Router]
    AUD --> APIA
    SYS --> APIA

    APIA --> DBA[(🗄️ User/Session/Audit models)]
    APII --> DBC[(🗄️ IntegrationConfig)]

    DBA --> ENF[🔐 Runtime Enforcement\nAuth dependency checks]
    DBC --> MAT[🔗 Matching processor ERP selection]

    ENF --> APP[🖥️ Protected App Flows]
    MAT --> PIPE[📄 Document processing pipeline]

%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
%% DIAGRAM 4 (Future): Edge AI Processing + Cloud Orchestration
%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
flowchart LR
    CAM[📷 Scanner/Mobile Capture] --> EDGEIN[🧩 Edge Ingestion SDK]
    EDGEIN --> PRE[⚡ On-device preprocess\ncrop, denoise, redact]
    PRE --> EOCR[🧠 Edge OCR + lightweight extraction]

    EOCR --> DEC{🌐 Connectivity available?}
    DEC -- No --> CACHE[(💾 Encrypted edge queue)]
    CACHE --> SYNC[🔄 Deferred sync agent]
    DEC -- Yes --> SYNC

    SYNC --> APIE[☁️ Cloud API ingress]
    APIE --> ORCH[⚙️ Cloud orchestrator]
    ORCH --> HEAVY[🤖 Heavy AI models\nvalidation, anomaly, risk]
    ORCH --> ERPF[🏢 ERP/finance integrations]
    ORCH --> WF[📋 Workflow + approval engine]

    HEAVY --> FB[📬 Model feedback package]
    WF --> FB
    FB --> EDGEUPD[📦 Edge model/rule update service]
    EDGEUPD --> EDGEIN

%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
%% DIAGRAM 5 (Future): Event-Driven Architecture + Multi-Agent Layer
%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
flowchart TD
    UI2[👤 User Actions\nupload, approve, resolve, batch submit] --> CMD[🛎️ Command API]
    CMD --> EVT[📡 Event Bus\nKafka/SNS/SQS or equivalent]

    EVT --> AG1[🤖 Agent: Extraction]
    EVT --> AG2[🤖 Agent: Compliance]
    EVT --> AG3[🤖 Agent: Matching]
    EVT --> AG4[🤖 Agent: Payment Optimization]
    EVT --> AG5[🤖 Agent: Fraud/Anomaly]

    AG1 --> ST1[(🗃️ Document events store)]
    AG2 --> ST2[(🗃️ Compliance events store)]
    AG3 --> ST3[(🗃️ Matching events store)]
    AG4 --> ST4[(🗃️ Payment events store)]
    AG5 --> ST5[(🗃️ Risk events store)]

    ST1 --> PROJ[📊 Read-model projector]
    ST2 --> PROJ
    ST3 --> PROJ
    ST4 --> PROJ
    ST5 --> PROJ

    PROJ --> APIQ[🔎 Query API\ndashboard KPIs + timeline views]
    APIQ --> UI2

    AG5 --> ESC{🚨 High-risk detected?}
    ESC -- Yes --> HIL[👨‍⚖️ Human-in-the-loop queue]
    HIL --> CMD

%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
%% DIAGRAM 6 (Future): Observability, Security, and Reliability Fabric
%% -------------------------------------------------------------------
flowchart TB
    APP2[🖥️ Frontend + API + Agents + Edge] --> OTEL[🛰️ OpenTelemetry collectors]
    OTEL --> LOGS[(📚 Logs)]
    OTEL --> MET[(📈 Metrics)]
    OTEL --> TRC[(🧭 Traces)]

    LOGS --> SIEM[🛡️ SIEM/SOC pipeline]
    MET --> APM[📉 APM + SLO engine]
    TRC --> APM

    SIEM --> DET[🚨 Threat detection rules]
    DET --> RESP[🔒 Automated response\nrevoke tokens, isolate device, step-up auth]

    APM --> REL{📛 Error budget burn?}
    REL -- Yes --> CB[⛔ Circuit breakers + feature flags]
    REL -- Yes --> SCALE[📈 Autoscaling + queue backpressure]
    REL -- No --> OK[✅ Normal operation]

    RESP --> GOV[📜 Immutable audit ledger]
    CB --> GOV
    SCALE --> GOV
